WayfindingNodeManager API

Packages 
Package Description
nodemanager
The only class this package contains is the NodeManager class, which serves as the entry point and controller for the program.
nodemanager.events
This package handles events, which are used to support undo and redo.
nodemanager.exceptions  
nodemanager.files
This package handles file helpers, which tell how to read and write the imports and exports of Wayfinding data.
nodemanager.gui
this package handles all the Graphic User Interface components the program uses, though it also has some back-end stuff in these components, which isn't good.
nodemanager.gui.editPage  
nodemanager.gui.editPage.mapComponents  
nodemanager.gui.exportData  
nodemanager.gui.importData  
nodemanager.io
this package contains some Input and Output functions used by a few other classes.
nodemanager.model
this package handles the data, or model of the program.
nodemanager.modes
Modes tell the program what to do when the user interacts with the MapImage.
